features: KLEEN HANDLER Heavy Duty Mop Head, Blue Mop Head Replacement, Pack of 3 Mopheads (Medium, 16 oz)

DURABILITY & MATERIAL – 16 oz. replacement mop head, 4-ply twist yarn made from cotton and blended fibers for scratch free, wet, and dry mopping. Excellent water absorption & retention, for effective floor cleaning and drying, an ideal balance of performance, durability & appearance. Commercial mop heads are durable and safe to use on all hard surfaces.

DESIGNED FOR FUNCTION – Looped end mop reduces fraying, virtually eliminating lint and untwisting of string mops! The time saver tail band makes cleaning more efficient! The looped mop design reduces friction between the floor, so that the mop glides rather than drags smoothly over the surface. While also improving the cleaning performance providing greater coverage for fast and efficient use.

UNIVERSAL FIT – Universal headband fits clamp style and side loading mop handles (sold separately). The headband resists moisture retention so the mop head can dry between uses. Heavy duty mop heads are for commercial, industrial, and residential use. The all purpose mop is suitable for: industrial cleaning, commercial cleaning, janitorial supplies, and household environments.

WASHABLE INDUSTRIAL MOP HEAD – Absorbent mop heads are launderable for extended long-term usage. The looped-end yarn design enhances productivity and is durable for machine washing. Long-lasting fibers allow the mop head to be washed many times giving it a longer service life. This washable mophead is launderable up to 100 times!

USED FOR VARIOUS ENVIRONMENTS: Cotton mop head designed for floor cleaning in commercial, industrial, and residential use. Perfect for a janitorial mop, mop head refills, heavy duty cleaning mops, mophead replacements, etc!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great purchase at a great price.
reviews.reviewText: When I mop I mop. These are real mop heads. We have both children and animals in the house. So, when we need to clean we need mops that are up to the task. With one of these and my good old mop bucket with wringer I can clean anything.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars SHEDS like crazy!
reviews.reviewText: I purchased these for a vet’s office. I needed mop heads that could withstand many washes and clean leaving minimal water behind.Pros: They’re relatively durable so far, not super heavy and the floors dry quickly.Cons: MAJOR SHEDDING problem! Even after several cycles in the washing machine, these mop heads still leave fuzzy blobs everywhere- on the floor, in the bucket, in the washing machine! FYI, these mop heads don’t dry quickly when on a mop handle; they can get mildewed if left sitting overnight after being squeezed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Washable and absorbent
reviews.reviewText: This 3 pack comes with each mop head individually vacuum sealed in space efficient wrap. Once opened, the mop heads are your standard commercial loop style mop. The fibers are soft and highly absorbent. This style of head works with a range of mop heads but check compatibility before buying. The benefit of these heads is that they are absorbent, inexpensive, and machine washable / easily renewed and reused. These 'commercial' style heads hold more water, mop up more mess, and make moping move faster than most 'residential' heads which are smaller and less durable. The only 'issue' is that the dirty head takes FOREVER to dry out so you need somewhere to store a damp/dirty head until you reuse or wash. No way around that but good to plan accordingly.
